that's where the shift changes.

00:35:23.290 --> 00:35:25.810 align:middle line:90%
That's where the shift occurs.

00:35:25.810 --> 00:35:27.660 align:middle line:84%
So you move from
the physicality--

00:35:27.660 --> 00:35:34.770 align:middle line:84%
from the ethical-- so society
and how you react and act--

00:35:34.770 --> 00:35:36.210 align:middle line:90%
interact with other people.

00:35:36.210 --> 00:35:38.778 align:middle line:84%
And then you move into
pranayama, the breathwork.

00:35:38.778 --> 00:35:40.320 align:middle line:84%
And that's where
you start to connect

00:35:40.320 --> 00:35:42.990 align:middle line:84%
the body and the
physicality and society

00:35:42.990 --> 00:35:46.360 align:middle line:90%
to a higher spiritual level--

00:35:46.360 --> 00:35:47.380 align:middle line:90%
meditation.

00:35:47.380 --> 00:35:51.670 align:middle line:84%
So awareness, and a
more broad awareness.

00:35:51.670 --> 00:35:56.920 align:middle line:84%
And the thing I'm trying
to bring into the world

00:35:56.920 --> 00:35:58.785 align:middle line:84%
is the part of
holding your breath.

00:35:58.785 --> 00:36:00.910 align:middle line:84%
Because no matter what
happens in your life and you

00:36:00.910 --> 00:36:02.690 align:middle line:84%
have stress-- if you
hold your breath,

00:36:02.690 --> 00:36:04.210 align:middle line:90%
