00:36:14.190 --> 00:36:15.327 align:middle line:90%
Why?

00:36:15.327 --> 00:36:16.660 align:middle line:90%
Because the brain is not moving.

00:36:16.660 --> 00:36:19.750 align:middle line:84%
It's not in that middle
of the boxing match.

00:36:19.750 --> 00:36:22.500 align:middle line:84%
It's not getting knocked
down all the time,

00:36:22.500 --> 00:36:25.860 align:middle line:84%
