and time to feel the body.

00:36:25.860 --> 00:36:29.832 align:middle line:84%
And the body is then balanced
in the feedback loop.

00:36:29.832 --> 00:36:31.290 align:middle line:84%
Then you can think
of other things.

00:36:31.290 --> 00:36:34.060 align:middle line:84%
That's why-- and I call
it meditation under water.

00:36:34.060 --> 00:36:35.880 align:middle line:84%
But that's just
something I call it.

