01:07:08.457 --> 01:07:10.290 align:middle line:84%
which is everything
that we've talked about,

01:07:10.290 --> 01:07:11.870 align:middle line:90%
moving to the next level--

01:07:11.870 --> 01:07:17.430 align:middle line:84%
your cells, your mind, what you
eat, people you hang out with--

01:07:17.430 --> 01:07:21.090 align:middle line:84%
and move that breathing
and the conscious breathing

01:07:21.090 --> 01:07:24.360 align:middle line:84%
up towards 80%, 90%, 100%
so every breath you take

01:07:24.360 --> 01:07:27.180 align:middle line:84%
is living your life
to the fullest.

01:07:27.180 --> 01:07:29.840 align:middle line:84%
Meaning that your cells
are working optimally.

01:07:29.840 --> 01:07:31.620 align:middle line:90%
You're digesting much better.

01:07:31.620 --> 01:07:35.850 align:middle line:84%
You're not keeping and
holding on to waste products.

01:07:35.850 --> 01:07:39.240 align:middle line:84%
You can also lose weight
easier because you're not

01:07:39.240 --> 01:07:40.890 align:middle line:90%
in a panic mode.

01:07:40.890 --> 01:07:46.170 align:middle line:84%
You're more open and
loving towards yourself.

01:07:46.170 --> 01:07:49.860 align:middle line:84%
And breathing, because it's
soft, also softens your mind

01:07:49.860 --> 01:07:52.710 align:middle line:90%
