know what you don't want to do.

01:10:31.790 --> 01:10:33.070 align:middle line:90%
That's my honest opinion.

01:10:33.070 --> 01:10:35.730 align:middle line:84%
If you are doing
something you don't like,

01:10:35.730 --> 01:10:38.910 align:middle line:84%
something you don't
love, stop it.

01:10:38.910 --> 01:10:41.430 align:middle line:90%
Why would you keep doing it?

01:10:41.430 --> 01:10:44.970 align:middle line:84%
But this is also like a
catch-22, tricky situation.

01:10:44.970 --> 01:10:48.810 align:middle line:84%
Because if you're a solo mom
with three kids and having

01:10:48.810 --> 01:10:51.750 align:middle line:84%
problems with your income and
just fighting to get everyday

01:10:51.750 --> 01:10:57.660 align:middle line:84%
life balancing, it's not the
first thing you wake up-- like,

01:10:57.660 --> 01:11:00.360 align:middle line:84%
oh, yeah, I have to help all
these people in the world today

01:11:00.360 --> 01:11:01.160 align:middle line:90%
and--

01:11:01.160 --> 01:11:03.810 align:middle line:84%
it would be a wonderful thought,
but you're just right here

01:11:03.810 --> 01:11:08.530 align:middle line:90%
in this difficult situation.

01:11:08.530 --> 01:11:11.290 align:middle line:84%
That will change,
hopefully, for anyone

01:11:11.290 --> 01:11:13.105 align:middle line:84%
in any part of the
world with time.

01:11:13.105 --> 01:11:16.620 align:middle line:90%


01:11:16.620 --> 01:11:21.358 align:middle line:84%
But for me, it's been a
really wandering road.

01:11:21.358 --> 01:11:22.650 align:middle line:90%
It's kind of like when I speak.

01:11:22.650 --> 01:11:25.560 align:middle line:84%
I speak about something and I
go in 5 different directions,

01:11:25.560 --> 01:11:26.745 align:middle line:90%
but I always come back.

01:11:26.745 --> 01:11:28.740 align:middle line:90%
So that is my strength.

01:11:28.740 --> 01:11:33.780 align:middle line:84%
And I think that is the
strength people should find,

01:11:33.780 --> 01:11:37.470 align:middle line:84%
is this stubbornness,
this continuity.

01:11:37.470 --> 01:11:40.950 align:middle line:84%
Just keep going, keep going,
and having the beliefs

01:11:40.950 --> 01:11:43.200 align:middle line:90%
that everything will be OK.

01:11:43.200 --> 01:11:45.960 align:middle line:90%
So I always loved animal.

01:11:45.960 --> 01:11:47.040 align:middle line:90%
I became a biologist.

01:11:47.040 --> 01:11:48.550 align:middle line:90%
There was no other way.

01:11:48.550 --> 01:11:49.350 align:middle line:90%
Again, I was lucky.

01:11:49.350 --> 01:11:51.267 align:middle line:84%
I was born in a country
I could get education.

01:11:51.267 --> 01:11:53.550 align:middle line:84%
I had wonderful
support in my family.

01:11:53.550 --> 01:11:56.390 align:middle line:84%
But I became a biologist because
I love nature and animals.

01:11:56.390 --> 01:11:58.620 align:middle line:84%
It's still the thing I
love the most in the world,

01:11:58.620 --> 01:12:02.400 align:middle line:84%
is watching animals; learn
about paleontology-- where

01:12:02.400 --> 01:12:05.160 align:middle line:84%
did we come from; learning
about how they communicate

01:12:05.160 --> 01:12:08.160 align:middle line:84%
because that translates to
so many other things in life.

01:12:08.160 --> 01:12:10.330 align:middle line:90%
Then I studied medicine.

01:12:10.330 --> 01:12:12.360 align:middle line:84%
I always had the swimming
and the freediving,

01:12:12.360 --> 01:12:13.920 align:middle line:84%
but that became
more professional.

01:12:13.920 --> 01:12:15.690 align:middle line:84%
Then I became ill
when I was a child.

01:12:15.690 --> 01:12:17.450 align:middle line:90%
I had severe asthma.

01:12:17.450 --> 01:12:19.350 align:middle line:84%
And that subconsciously
probably led

01:12:19.350 --> 01:12:21.450 align:middle line:84%
me to reflect more on
breathing and the importance

01:12:21.450 --> 01:12:23.580 align:middle line:90%
of proper breathing.

01:12:23.580 --> 01:12:26.850 align:middle line:84%
And then in science, and
my journeys to India,

01:12:26.850 --> 01:12:30.300 align:middle line:90%
and my peak performance sport--

01:12:30.300 --> 01:12:33.240 align:middle line:90%
so the freediving records--

01:12:33.240 --> 01:12:36.850 align:middle line:84%
brought that breath holding
aspect into the completeness

01:12:36.850 --> 01:12:37.650 align:middle line:90%
of breathwork.

01:12:37.650 --> 01:12:40.470 align:middle line:84%
So that's when I created this
framework of Breatheology.

01:12:40.470 --> 01:12:41.970 align:middle line:84%
Because there was
something missing.

01:12:41.970 --> 01:12:43.560 align:middle line:84%
If you are just
breathing, breathing

01:12:43.560 --> 01:12:45.930 align:middle line:90%
is actually stressful.

01:12:45.930 --> 01:12:47.280 align:middle line:90%
Taking the breath is stressful.

01:12:47.280 --> 01:12:49.260 align:middle line:90%
The exhale is what relaxes you.

01:12:49.260 --> 01:12:51.700 align:middle line:84%
I always tell people
the key to relaxation

01:12:51.700 --> 01:12:54.970 align:middle line:90%
is in the exhalation.

01:12:54.970 --> 01:13:00.220 align:middle line:84%
So I think for people to not
do what they were meant to do,

01:13:00.220 --> 01:13:04.322 align:middle line:84%
or this greater purpose,
is a waste of life.

01:13:04.322 --> 01:13:06.030 align:middle line:84%
And where do you find
that purpose, then?

01:13:06.030 --> 01:13:07.738 align:middle line:84%
For me, it's helping
the world to breathe

01:13:07.738 --> 01:13:09.240 align:middle line:90%
better, one breath at a time.

01:13:09.240 --> 01:13:11.730 align:middle line:84%
When you find that
purpose, you against

01:13:11.730 --> 01:13:14.730 align:middle line:84%
start to visualize and dream
and look for people that

01:13:14.730 --> 01:13:16.830 align:middle line:90%
can help you and support you.

01:13:16.830 --> 01:13:18.000 align:middle line:90%
And you move forward.

01:13:18.000 --> 01:13:19.980 align:middle line:84%
And you move five
steps backwards.

01:13:19.980 --> 01:13:21.610 align:middle line:90%
And then again, you push.

01:13:21.610 --> 01:13:26.540 align:middle line:90%
And it's this ongoing journey.

01:13:26.540 --> 01:13:31.548 align:middle line:84%
And then when you start to see
the results and the change,

01:13:31.548 --> 01:13:32.840 align:middle line:90%
that is the biggest fulfilling.

01:13:32.840 --> 01:13:34.400 align:middle line:90%
So that is fulfillment in life.

01:13:34.400 --> 01:13:40.010 align:middle line:84%
That is being gifted with
all these wonderful stories

01:13:40.010 --> 01:13:42.350 align:middle line:84%
of people's lives
you have changed,

01:13:42.350 --> 01:13:47.640 align:middle line:84%
from a simple thing as breathing
or from changing the mindset.

01:13:47.640 --> 01:13:50.150 align:middle line:84%
And I have no doubt
that breathing

01:13:50.150 --> 01:13:54.020 align:middle line:84%
will be the next revolution,
everything-- in science,

01:13:54.020 --> 01:13:59.250 align:middle line:84%
in medicine, in prevention, in
treatment, and rehabilitation.

01:13:59.250 --> 01:14:03.570 align:middle line:84%
So in all aspects of
the health care system,

01:14:03.570 --> 01:14:05.050 align:middle line:84%
breathing will be
a big, big part.

01:14:05.050 --> 01:14:07.875 align:middle line:84%
And I also think for
children and schools-- that's

01:14:07.875 --> 01:14:09.250 align:middle line:84%
one of my big
missions, as well--

01:14:09.250 --> 01:14:10.792 align:middle line:84%
to get to yoga,
breathing, meditation

01:14:10.792 --> 01:14:14.530 align:middle line:84%
into every single
school of the world.

01:14:14.530 --> 01:14:18.443 align:middle line:84%
Because if you as a child
learn to breathe consciously,

01:14:18.443 --> 01:14:20.110 align:middle line:84%
then you don't have
all these challenges

01:14:20.110 --> 01:14:23.860 align:middle line:84%
that we're facing now, and you
don't have all those issues

01:14:23.860 --> 01:14:28.000 align:middle line:84%
with stress and illness to
this same extreme degree

01:14:28.000 --> 01:14:30.280 align:middle line:84%
as we're seeing
now in the world.

01:14:30.280 --> 01:14:35.230 align:middle line:84%
And that is creating good
habits and creating a stronger

01:14:35.230 --> 01:14:37.850 align:middle line:84%
relationship with
yourself and nature.

01:14:37.850 --> 01:14:40.930 align:middle line:84%
And I think the easiest way to
find your purpose is actually

01:14:40.930 --> 01:14:46.440 align:middle line:84%
to tune into your true nature,
because you have it in you.

01:14:46.440 --> 01:14:49.640 align:middle line:84%
It's not-- I don't know
where it comes from.

01:14:49.640 --> 01:14:52.460 align:middle line:84%
Couldn't say it's in your genes,
but it's probably passed down

01:14:52.460 --> 01:14:55.790 align:middle line:90%
from generations to you.

01:14:55.790 --> 01:14:57.320 align:middle line:84%
Different skills,
different things

01:14:57.320 --> 01:15:01.590 align:middle line:84%
that were important to
survive, different tactics,

01:15:01.590 --> 01:15:06.490 align:middle line:84%
different ways of thinking,
all this is passed down to you.

01:15:06.490 --> 01:15:08.240 align:middle line:84%
And then of course
there's the environment

01:15:08.240 --> 01:15:11.430 align:middle line:84%
and the way you train your mind
and take care of your body.

01:15:11.430 --> 01:15:13.490 align:middle line:84%
So whether you have found
your purpose or not,

01:15:13.490 --> 01:15:15.610 align:middle line:90%
you should keep searching.

01:15:15.610 --> 01:15:19.223 align:middle line:84%
Whether you have found
your purpose in life or not

01:15:19.223 --> 01:15:20.140 align:middle line:90%
doesn't really matter.

01:15:20.140 --> 01:15:23.380 align:middle line:84%
You should hopefully find
it at some point, the sooner

01:15:23.380 --> 01:15:27.400 align:middle line:84%
the better, so you can serve and
help other people around you.

01:15:27.400 --> 01:15:32.050 align:middle line:84%
And you get a tremendous amount
of love and thankfulness back.

01:15:32.050 --> 01:15:36.400 align:middle line:84%
And this is what will bring
fulfillment in your life.

01:15:36.400 --> 01:15:40.690 align:middle line:84%
So for me, starting as
a child with asthma,

01:15:40.690 --> 01:15:44.532 align:middle line:84%
becoming a scientist, doing
my PhD degree in medicine,

01:15:44.532 --> 01:15:46.240 align:middle line:84%
moving into more
professional freediving,

01:15:46.240 --> 01:15:47.590 align:middle line:90%
setting world records--

01:15:47.590 --> 01:15:51.130 align:middle line:84%
Guinness World Records--
breaking these limiting beliefs

01:15:51.130 --> 01:15:53.873 align:middle line:84%
and showing the world
that in my world,

01:15:53.873 --> 01:15:56.040 align:middle line:84%
breath holding for more
than 20 minutes is possible,

01:15:56.040 --> 01:15:58.630 align:middle line:90%
diving under ice is possible--

01:15:58.630 --> 01:16:04.010 align:middle line:84%
all those things
have meant nothing

01:16:04.010 --> 01:16:06.800 align:middle line:84%
if I didn't succeed
in translating

01:16:06.800 --> 01:16:11.730 align:middle line:84%
all that into something that
brings purpose to other people.

01:16:11.730 --> 01:16:13.910 align:middle line:90%
So for me, it's breathwork.

01:16:13.910 --> 01:16:17.120 align:middle line:84%
So it's helping people to
become more aware of breath,

01:16:17.120 --> 01:16:19.760 align:middle line:84%
the power of breath, how
they can cure themselves,

01:16:19.760 --> 01:16:23.660 align:middle line:84%
treat themselves for
stress, different diseases.

01:16:23.660 --> 01:16:26.660 align:middle line:84%
But it's also bringing in the
aspect of breath holding--

01:16:26.660 --> 01:16:28.640 align:middle line:90%
so pausing.

01:16:28.640 --> 01:16:31.430 align:middle line:84%
So it's also a metaphor
for just taking a break.

01:16:31.430 --> 01:16:32.230 align:middle line:90%
Relax.

01:16:32.230 --> 01:16:33.760 align:middle line:90%
It's going to be OK.

01:16:33.760 --> 01:16:35.260 align:middle line:84%
And when you combine
the breathing--

01:16:35.260 --> 01:16:37.720 align:middle line:84%
the energy, the life
force-- and the breath

01:16:37.720 --> 01:16:40.780 align:middle line:84%
holding-- the pause, the
giving in, the letting go,

01:16:40.780 --> 01:16:43.490 align:middle line:84%
the acceptance of
death, basically--

01:16:43.490 --> 01:16:45.050 align:middle line:84%
and you bring
those two together,

01:16:45.050 --> 01:16:47.710 align:middle line:90%
you have balance in life.

01:16:47.710 --> 01:16:50.380 align:middle line:84%
So for me, purpose
is the fulfillment

01:16:50.380 --> 01:16:52.990 align:middle line:84%
of helping millions
of other people--

01:16:52.990 --> 01:16:54.790 align:middle line:90%
which I'm already doing now--

01:16:54.790 --> 01:16:58.150 align:middle line:84%
discover the unlimited
power of breathwork.

01:16:58.150 --> 01:16:59.710 align:middle line:84%
Another thing that's
very important

01:16:59.710 --> 01:17:01.240 align:middle line:84%
when you talk about
purpose in life

01:17:01.240 --> 01:17:03.970 align:middle line:84%
is that you should always
believe in yourself.

01:17:03.970 --> 01:17:07.020 align:middle line:84%
Don't think that your
dream is too small,

01:17:07.020 --> 01:17:08.020 align:middle line:90%
that it's not important.

01:17:08.020 --> 01:17:12.412 align:middle line:84%
Because what I've seen with all
the wonderful, talented, loving

01:17:12.412 --> 01:17:13.870 align:middle line:84%
people I've met
around the world is

01:17:13.870 --> 01:17:18.568 align:middle line:84%
that what holds people
back-- of course

01:17:18.568 --> 01:17:20.610 align:middle line:84%
it's a limiting belief
that they're not important

01:17:20.610 --> 01:17:23.660 align:middle line:84%
or their hobby, their passion,
is not important enough.

01:17:23.660 --> 01:17:27.650 align:middle line:84%
But when you start to look
at the bigger picture--

01:17:27.650 --> 01:17:28.657 align:middle line:90%
let's take my example.

01:17:28.657 --> 01:17:29.990 align:middle line:90%
So I help people breathe better.

01:17:29.990 --> 01:17:30.550 align:middle line:90%
Who cares?

01:17:30.550 --> 01:17:32.258 align:middle line:84%
OK, he was breathing
a little bit better.

01:17:32.258 --> 01:17:34.220 align:middle line:90%
No.

01:17:34.220 --> 01:17:36.620 align:middle line:84%
I help one person
to breathe better--

01:17:36.620 --> 01:17:39.200 align:middle line:84%
it could be from a traumatic
event, could be from stress,

01:17:39.200 --> 01:17:42.260 align:middle line:84%
could be from PTSD, it
could be from illness--

01:17:42.260 --> 01:17:43.850 align:middle line:90%
what happens then?

01:17:43.850 --> 01:17:45.660 align:middle line:84%
That whole family
starts to heal.

01:17:45.660 --> 01:17:47.030 align:middle line:90%
Right?

01:17:47.030 --> 01:17:48.710 align:middle line:90%
What happens then?

01:17:48.710 --> 01:17:50.300 align:middle line:84%
The kid has an easier
time at school,

01:17:50.300 --> 01:17:52.370 align:middle line:84%
focusing on the homework,
getting better grades,

01:17:52.370 --> 01:17:53.245 align:middle line:90%
getting an education.

01:17:53.245 --> 01:17:54.710 align:middle line:90%
What happens then?

01:17:54.710 --> 01:17:56.810 align:middle line:84%
The whole neighborhood
starts to--

01:17:56.810 --> 01:17:58.910 align:middle line:90%
they have a party at summer.

01:17:58.910 --> 01:18:01.670 align:middle line:84%
Then they can be resourceful
and bring some food.

01:18:01.670 --> 01:18:02.670 align:middle line:90%
What happens then?

01:18:02.670 --> 01:18:04.880 align:middle line:90%
It spreads out of the community.

01:18:04.880 --> 01:18:09.950 align:middle line:84%
So what I'm trying to say is
that when you find your purpose

01:18:09.950 --> 01:18:13.520 align:middle line:84%
in life, stick with that
and believe in yourself,

01:18:13.520 --> 01:18:16.370 align:middle line:84%
because you need to believe so
much in yourself that you also

01:18:16.370 --> 01:18:17.960 align:middle line:90%
convince other people.

01:18:17.960 --> 01:18:20.550 align:middle line:84%
And then good
things will happen.

01:18:20.550 --> 01:18:23.030 align:middle line:84%
So it's a rippling
effect, I'm talking about,

01:18:23.030 --> 01:18:23.960 align:middle line:90%
from your passion.

01:18:23.960 --> 01:18:27.440 align:middle line:84%
Because that translate--
passion, I think,

01:18:27.440 --> 01:18:29.440 align:middle line:84%
is one of the strongest
driving force in life.

01:18:29.440 --> 01:18:30.880 align:middle line:90%
Passion is also love.

01:18:30.880 --> 01:18:35.130 align:middle line:84%
Passion is giving love
to one area in your life,

01:18:35.130 --> 01:18:39.680 align:middle line:84%
whether it's arts or
nature or architecture--

01:18:39.680 --> 01:18:43.460 align:middle line:84%
anything in life that you
spend your precious time on.

01:18:43.460 --> 01:18:45.770 align:middle line:84%
And that is why passion
is so powerful, because it

01:18:45.770 --> 01:18:51.950 align:middle line:84%
translates, it travels through
the creation of your work

01:18:51.950 --> 01:18:55.340 align:middle line:90%
to other people on many levels.

01:18:55.340 --> 01:18:58.880 align:middle line:90%
And art is a good example.

01:18:58.880 --> 01:19:01.300 align:middle line:84%
The beauty-- and
sport, of course, also.

01:19:01.300 --> 01:19:03.170 align:middle line:90%
The peak performance.

01:19:03.170 --> 01:19:04.610 align:middle line:84%
Maybe people don't
understand it,

01:19:04.610 --> 01:19:08.570 align:middle line:84%
but there is a message that
travels and reaches them.

01:19:08.570 --> 01:19:10.520 align:middle line:84%
That's why when you see
the pain in athletes

01:19:10.520 --> 01:19:13.010 align:middle line:84%
or you see the victory,
you identify yourself

01:19:13.010 --> 01:19:16.080 align:middle line:84%
in that, but maybe in
your life struggle, maybe

01:19:16.080 --> 01:19:18.172 align:middle line:90%
your financial situation.

01:19:18.172 --> 01:19:19.130 align:middle line:90%
So you're not a runner.

01:19:19.130 --> 01:19:21.200 align:middle line:84%
OK, you didn't run
a marathon, but you

01:19:21.200 --> 01:19:23.960 align:middle line:84%
have been working nine
to five for 12 years,

01:19:23.960 --> 01:19:26.330 align:middle line:84%
supporting three kids,
so that's a marathon.

01:19:26.330 --> 01:19:32.980 align:middle line:84%
So I think when people stick
to what they love and find

01:19:32.980 --> 01:19:36.070 align:middle line:84%
that purpose, it will
help the world change.

01:19:36.070 --> 01:19:39.120 align:middle line:90%
